    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Using a host of clones to improve the efficiency of your training. When you start to learn a technique, you may spend an Action Point to gain +10 to the Learn check, and reduce the time per attempt by half (before applying time reductions from your Learn check result). This does not apply to mastering techniques.<br><br>If used, you suffer 40d6 nonlethal damage at the end of the training day (or 20d6 if only half a day was spent), though the damage cannot exceed your maximum hp.<br><br>Note: This training technique is extremely powerful and should be denied to player characters.</p>\n\n\n\n",
